data.description: Welcome to this immaculate one-story home with 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, an office, and everything you need for comfortable living. This move-in-ready gem is conveniently located on the same street as the neighborhood pool and amenity center, making recreation and relaxation easily accessible. Nestled in a friendly community, it boasts Clear Springs Elementary within close proximity. The kitchen is a delightful highlight, radiating brightness and airiness, equipped with stainless steel appliances, beautiful granite countertops, and an inviting island for culinary delights. The bedrooms are all generously sized, ensuring ample space for everyone. The primary suite comes complete with an ensuite featuring a large walk-in shower and dual sinks for added convenience. Additionally, the home is pre-plumbed for a water softener and features an irrigation system to keep the lawn looking lush and healthy. Don't miss the chance to see this exceptional property for yourself!
